msgid ""
"If you are outside the US, we recommend NOWPayments (lowest fees, direct to "
"your wallet). If you are in the US, Stripe Crypto is also an option. You can"
" enable multiple services and let your visitors choose!"
msgstr ""
"Soki ozali na mokanda ya US, tozo koyeba NOWPayments (balingo ya minene, "
"tozo na wallet na yo). Soki ozali na US, Stripe Crypto ezali mpo na "
"bosungisi. Onzozola service esolo mpe okoki koyokola ba bakonzi na yo "
"balobela!"

